 />\n香港既權貴們有無為香港發聲？不論係枱面定枱底，麻煩你地為香港為自己出聲，要不然到權貴們都出事既時候，我怕無人再為你出聲了! ......話口未完，<span style=\"color: blue;\">誠哥又剛用左幾百億買左英國Greene King (Pub Chain)，飲英國啤酒</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔撚駛理香港同中國</strong></span>!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af69d02331ff6fa5a3852ce45be68c677fb87b46","tid":1492863,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:27:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">【眾籌 Google 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aeNRkiU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aeNRkiU</a>"},{"pid":"e048ad2bd23445a74d9b15b44a0e92d17092c4b2","tid":1492863,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:36:57.000Z","msg":"完全冇一個有power既人保護香港"},{"pid":"43e2d6111d600ec654098322d6dec26a396ea7d3","tid":1492863,"uid":300221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T10:58:11.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">到機管局了</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190821&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59957672\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190821%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59957672&d=DXuv2gayA%2Byyjyt3RGK41JriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=22e0727d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190821%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59957672&h=2c273c27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190821&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59957672</a><br />\n<br />\n【逆權運動】航空業白色恐怖未止 機管局急炒兩名經理級管理人員"}]}